        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <div id="content">
        <div class="row" id="cant-be-bought">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <header>
                    <h1>Can't Be Bought</h1>
                </header>
                <p>There are more slaves in the world today than ever before. Surprised? We were too. Continue scrolling to learn join-the-fight what's going on, and how you can help stop it.</p>
                <nav class="next-prev">
                    <hr />
                    <a class="next another-life" href="#another-life">Next</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" id="another-life">
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <header>
                    <h1>21 MILLION</h1>
                </header>
                <p>people are enslaved in the world today. <br>Human trafficking is the modern day slave trade.<br>In the USA alone, 208 people will be trafficked today.<br>Click on someone and experience their story.</p>
                <nav class="next-prev">
                    <a class="prev cant-be-bought" href="#cant-be-bought">Prev</a>
                    <hr />
                    <a class="next the-statistics" href="#the-statistics">Next</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <div class="dashboard-view-container">
                    <div class="dashboard-ui-view" ui-view></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row" id="the-statistics">
            <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
                <header>
                    <h1>The Statistics</h1>
                </header>

                <div class="row graphs">
                    <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="selectGraph('graph1')">Graph 1</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="selectGraph('graph2')">Graph 2</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="selectGraph('graph3')">Graph 3</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="selectGraph('graph4')">Graph 4</button>
                
                    <div ng-switch on="selectedGraph">
                      <div ng-switch-when="graph1">
                        <div class="graph1 text-center" ng-controller="graph1">
                              <h1>Graph 1 Section</h1>
                              <div id="graph1" style="width:60%; height:600px; margin: 0 auto;"></div>
                          </div>
                      </div>

                      <div ng-switch-when="graph2">
                          <div class="graph2 text-center" ng-controller="graph2">
                              <h1>Graph 2 Section</h1>
                              <div id="graph2" style="width:60%; height:400px; margin: 0 auto;"></div>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div ng-switch-when="graph3">
                        <div class="graph3 text-center" ng-controller="graph3">
                          <div id="graph3" style="width:60%; height:600px; background-color: white; margin: 0 auto;"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div ng-switch-when="graph4">
                        <div class="graph4 text-center" ng-controller="graph4">
                            <h1>Graph 4 Section</h1>
                            <div id="graph4" style="min-width: 310px; min-height: 700px; max-height: 900px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>  <!-- ng-switch -->
                </div>

                <nav class="next-prev">
                    <a class="prev another-life" href="#another-life">Prev</a>
                    <hr />
                    <a class="next video" href="#video">Next</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" id="video">
            <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
            <header>
                <h1>Video</h1>
            </header>
                <div class="row video">
                    <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
                        <h1>Video Section</h1>
                        <iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/114795036" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> <p><a href="http://vimeo.com/114795036">try dec 17</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/user33950663">amanda raymond</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="getSelectedStatistic();" class="col-sm-12">Click for Fact</button>
                        <div ng-show="selectedStatistic">   
                            <div class="video text-center"><h1>{{selectedStatistic.sentence}}</h1></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <nav class="next-prev">
                <a class="prev the-statistics" href="#the-statistics">Prev</a>
                <hr />
                <a class="next join-the-fight" href="#join-the-fight">Next</a>
            </nav>
            </div>
        </div>        
        
        <div class="row" id="join-the-fight">
            <header>
                <h1>Join the Fight</h1>
            </header>
            <p>On this page you can click and find out what happened to the person you learned join-the-fight above.  You can also get in contact with organizations, ways to donate, and access to more reports.</p>
            <div class="row about">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <div class="text-center">
                       <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="revealTransport();">Click to see where you ended up</button>
                       <p>{{transport}}<p>
                       <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="revealFate();">Click to reveal if you were res</button>
                       <p>{{fate}}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <nav class="next-prev">
                <a class="prev the-statistics" href="#the-statistics">Prev</a>
                <hr />
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
